b4 shazam [\-h] [\-p USEPROJECT] [\-m LOCALMBOX] [\-C] [\-v WANTVER] [\-t] [\-S] [\-T] [\-s] [\-l] [\-P CHERRYPICK] [\-\-cc\-trailers] [\-\-no\-parent] [\-\-allow\-unicode\-control\-chars] [\-H | \-M] [\-\-guess\-lookback GUESSDAYS] [msgid]
